
Model of layer link protocol of the IEEE-1394

according to article "Verification of the Link layer protocol of the IEEE-1394 serial bus (FireWire)" (Sighireanu, Matescu)

manually translated from E-LOTOS (and description) to .mdve; with abstraction from data, header, ack. values

parameters:
N = number of nodes
APPLICATION -- ruzne scenare:
 	0 - posle se jen jedna zprava
	1 - kazdej posle jednu zpravu nasledujicimu
	2 - neomezene posilani zprav

properties:
to add (problem, protoze oni je maji action based a to se prevadi docela spatne)

Size:
BIG